# This is NOT a real CNAME file — it's a note for later.
#
# Once you've bought your domain, create a new file in this repo
# named exactly "CNAME" (no extension, no leading dot) containing
# ONLY your domain name on a single line, with nothing else in the
# file. For example, if your domain is yourschool.in and you want
# the site at www.yourschool.in, the file CNAME would contain
# exactly this one line:
#
# www.yourschool.in
#
# Delete this example file once the real CNAME file is in place.
